categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: This Imperial officer served under Captain Brunson along with a second officer in her Arquitens-class command cruiser, reporting anything that seemed unusual to her. He got slapped by Brunson when he told her that the rocket trooper squadron had suffered heavy losses.
He is voiced by Steve Blum who also voiced Garazeb Orrelios.
He shares the animation model and voice as Commander Woldar in "Zero Hour" and "Rebel Assault". It's unknown if this is Woldar or just a similar looking and sounding officer.[source?]
